def numerical_column_visualization(df):

    columns  =df.select_dtypes(include=np.number).columns.tolist()
    n=len(columns)
    fig, axs = plt.subplots(n,2,figsize=(20,30))
    
    for index,colum in enumerate(columns):
        sns.boxplot(data=df, x=colum ,ax=axs[index,0])
        sns.histplot(df[colum],ax=axs[index,1],kde=True)  
    fig.tight_layout()

def categorical_column_visualization(df):
    columns  =df.select_dtypes(exclude=np.number).columns.tolist()
    n=len(columns)
    fig, axs = plt.subplots(n,1,figsize=(10,15))
    
    for index,colum in enumerate(columns):
        sns.histplot(data=df, x=colum ,ax=axs[index]) 
    fig.tight_layout()

def encoding_categorical_ordinal(df,columns):
    ord_enc = OrdinalEncoder()
    for i in columns:
        df[i] = ord_enc.fit_transform(df[[i]])

    return  df

columns_to_encode=["Seasons","Holiday","FunctioningDay" , "LabelDayNight"]
